article.description: — Carl Pierre had 20 points as Rice defeated Southern 81-63 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Pierre scores 20 to carry Rice past Southern 81-63
article.linkText: Pierre scores 20 to carry Rice past Southern 81-63
article.story: HOUSTON -- — Carl Pierre had 20 points as Rice defeated Southern 81-63 on Tuesday night. Max Fiedler had 17 points for Rice (2-1). Travis Evee added 15 points. Chris Mullins had 13 points. Tyrone Lyons had 19 points for the Jaguars (1-2). Jayden Saddler added 12 points. Terrell Williams had 10 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
